<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_146_r1l23">frawn Elſpeten <expan>Marggrafin<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_146_r1l24">Gnedıge frawe Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etliche <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute <expan>fürbr<ex>aht</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l25">vvie ſie etvvaʒ treffenlıcher hab vnd kauffmanſchaft <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> auff der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l26">ſtraſʒe von preſʒlaw herauſʒ geen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l27">mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> Amptleuten vnd den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſchıcken vnd beſtellen wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l28">daʒ ſie deſter <expan>fleiſſig<ex>er</ex></expan> darob ſein . daʒ die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> habe vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l29">kauffmanſchaft . durch ewr land . herſchaft vnd gepıete ſicher </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l30">geleytet werden Als etc Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Marg<ex>arete</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_146" id="72r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawn Elspeten, <expan>marggrafin<ex>n</ex></expan> czu
                                                  <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige frawe, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etliche
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kauffleute
                                                  <expan>fürbr<ex>aht</ex></expan>, wie sie etwaz
                                                treffenlicher hab und kauffmanschaft
                                                  <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> auff der strasze
                                                von Preszlaw herausz geen
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir von
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> mit
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> amptleuten und den
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> schicken und
                                                bestellen wöllet, daz sie dester
                                                  <expan>fleissig<ex>er</ex></expan> darob sein, daz
                                                die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit
                                                  <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> habe und
                                                kauffmanschaft durch ewr land, herschaft und gepiete
                                                sicher geleytet werden als etc. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi
                                                  <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Marg<ex>arete</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
